$ devmgmt.msc

*Device Manager*

The device manager can be started in → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmdkey_exe[`cmd.exe`] by just typing `devmgmt.msc` or using → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/mmc_exe[`mmc.exe`]:
code {
C:\> devmgmt.msc
C:\> mmc devmgmt.msc
code }

gh|Windows-Pics|/Windows/System32/devmgmt.msc.png||

{ Disable Webcam #devmgmt-disable-webcam

  The device manager allows to disable a web cam.

  The web cam is found either under *Imaging Devices* -> *Integrated Camera* or *Cameras* -> *Integrated Webcam*

}
{ Environment variable _devmgr_show_nonpresent_devices

  Setting the → development/environment-variable[environment variable] `_devmgr_show_nonpresent_devices` to `1` before starting the device manager will cause the device manager to
  *show inactive devices* as well.

}

